      "id": "PopularPost231571",
      "post_content": "Would playing [Enchanted Evening](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Enchanted Evening) and this result in a draw?  \n  \nWhen you have 10 or less life, it would turn into a Creature. But it would turn into an Enchantment Creature, and thus try to turn into a creature again, and again, until one of them were destroyed or you went to 11 or more health.",
